'''''Celeg''''' is a [[Sindarin]] adjective meaning "swift" or "agile".
==Etymology==
Probably [[OS]] *''keleka'', from [[PQ]] *''kyelekâ'', [[Sundocarmë|Root]] [[KYELEK]]
== Examples ==
* [[Celegorm]] = Hasty-riser
*[[River Running|Celduin]]
